<hr />
<h2>4 · Write a Branch ✍️</h2>
<p>Add one more <code>elif</code> to the solver. When there is redstone straight <strong>ahead</strong>, the agent should turn <strong>right</strong> and move forward.</p>
<p><strong>Write the branch:</strong></p>
